data.description: Welcome home to this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located in the prestigious Carolina Trace golf community. This home was freshly painted, professionally cleaned, power washed, and is now move-in ready. The open floor welcomes an abundance of natural light in the large living room and kitchen. The kitchen features granite countertops and a new cook-top to match the stainless-steel appliances. All three bedrooms are located downstairs as well as the laundry room, with a washer and dryer to be conveyed. The stairs lead up to the loft that overlooks the dining area and kitchen. The exterior of this home features a large covered front porch, elevated deck, and outside storage. The home sits on a private lot at the end of a culde sac near one of the lakes. Schedule your showing and come see this stunning home!! Seller is offering $5,000 towards buyers closing costs with full price offer.
